label.text: - You start with 5 rolls on the "Roll" page. After your 5 rolls are out, watch at least 3 videos to reset them back to 5!
- You can view your collection so far in the "Collection" tab. To watch a video, simply tap on one of the videos.

label.string: - Your profile tab holds all the information you need to know. You may also choose a special profile picture by pressing "Edit Image". You may also sign out of the app if necessary.
